title: Texting Tutor PT 3: This Mom Is Demanding $250 After She Rescheduled A Kid's Party!
description:
It's a mom battle! She had to move her daughter's party and now another mom is formally requesting $250 for babysitting fees!
That’s where we come in! She wants our help politely explaining to her that she's DENYING that venmo request!
